        <section>

            <h2>Example</h2>

<pre>
import theia.math.Arithmetic;

double result = Arithmetic.Add(5, 3);

System.out.println(result);
</pre>

            <p>
                TheiaMath was designed with readability and simplicity in mind.
                Most operations can be performed through straightforward static
                methods.
            </p>

